00:22:11,940 --> 00:22:12,610
but ignorant.

596
00:22:13,180 --> 00:22:14,770
Don't stoop to my level.

597
00:22:15,660 --> 00:22:16,610
In terms of age,

598
00:22:16,850 --> 00:22:18,020
you are older than me.

599
00:22:18,330 --> 00:22:19,050
Seniority-wise,

600
00:22:19,180 --> 00:22:20,050
you are my uncle.

601
00:22:20,130 --> 00:22:20,770
Correct?

602
00:22:21,290 --> 00:22:22,740
A great man is kind and magnanimous.

603
00:22:24,290 --> 00:22:25,770
Let me tell you something practical.

604
00:22:26,290 --> 00:22:27,610
The village committee decided

605
00:22:28,090 --> 00:22:29,660
that your annual salary
as the Group's vice president

606
00:22:30,050 --> 00:22:30,900
will be 100,000 yuan more than mine.

607
00:22:31,130 --> 00:22:32,020
Is that okay?

608
00:22:32,700 --> 00:22:33,420
What?

609
00:22:34,330 --> 00:22:35,610
What 100,000 yuan?

610
00:22:36,460 --> 00:22:37,740
Not 100,000 yuan a year.

611
00:22:38,020 --> 00:22:39,660
It's 100,000 yuan more than me a year.

612
00:22:40,130 --> 00:22:41,180
Whatever my annual salary,

613
00:22:41,420 --> 00:22:42,660
you'll have 100,000 yuan more.

614
00:22:42,700 --> 00:22:43,530
When I get a raise, you get it too.

615
00:22:45,330 --> 00:22:47,090
This...

616
00:22:48,020 --> 00:22:49,940
This is inappropriate. Inappropriate.

617
00:22:50,220 --> 00:22:51,500
How so?

618
00:22:51,700 --> 00:22:52,220
It's appropriate.

619
00:22:53,290 --> 00:22:53,940
You see.

620
00:22:54,220 --> 00:22:54,940
The two villages

621
00:22:54,940 --> 00:22:56,740
are merging,

622
00:22:56,980 --> 00:22:59,020
but one is on the mountain
and one at the foothill.

623
00:22:59,500 --> 00:23:01,220
In the future, I'll rely on you

624
00:23:01,370 --> 00:23:03,330
to take overall charge

625
00:23:03,330 --> 00:23:04,900
of Shuiwei Village.

626
00:23:05,770 --> 00:23:07,660
You've been the village leader for many years,

627
00:23:07,810 --> 00:23:09,050
so you enjoy high prestige.

628
00:23:10,810 --> 00:23:11,500
Well.

629
00:23:12,940 --> 00:23:14,220
What about

630
00:23:14,700 --> 00:23:16,940
the village committee?

631
00:23:17,290 --> 00:23:18,530
For the village committee,

632
00:23:18,610 --> 00:23:19,610
it's the same for both villages.

633
00:23:19,980 --> 00:23:22,020
Everyone will have a grade according to

634
00:23:22,020 --> 00:23:23,050
his position and age.

635
00:23:24,700 --> 00:23:25,660
For example, Yanping,

636
00:23:25,660 --> 00:23:26,500
you should receive

637
00:23:27,020 --> 00:23:28,290
200,000 to 300,000 yuan per year.

638
00:23:28,810 --> 00:23:29,530
Really?

639
00:23:29,940 --> 00:23:30,770
Definitely.

640
00:23:31,130 --> 00:23:31,980
What about the villagers?

641
00:23:32,500 --> 00:23:33,570
The two villages, well...

642
00:23:34,290 --> 00:23:34,610
Hey,

643
00:23:34,740 --> 00:23:35,740
why did I say

644
00:23:35,740 --> 00:23:36,900
two villages?

645
00:23:37,090 --> 00:23:38,460
We are villagers of one village.

646
00:23:38,940 --> 00:23:41,020
Yes, we will merge and become a family.

647
00:23:41,020 --> 00:23:43,050
Family members are all equal.

648
00:23:43,050 --> 00:23:44,370
We are the same.

649
00:23:45,900 --> 00:23:46,700
In addition to that,

650
00:23:47,130 --> 00:23:49,290
I heard that in our village,

651
00:23:49,500 --> 00:23:51,460
the adults and kids of some families are sick.

652
00:23:52,180 --> 00:23:52,530
Yes.

653
00:23:52,530 --> 00:23:53,570
There is an uproar

654
00:23:53,740 --> 00:23:55,180
over water pollution caused by

655
00:23:55,570 --> 00:23:56,700
the health products factory.

656
00:23:58,180 --> 00:23:59,090
That's right.

657
00:23:59,740 --> 00:24:00,260
Take a look.

658
00:24:00,530 --> 00:24:01,020
This is...?

659
00:24:01,220 --> 00:24:01,810
These are

660
00:24:02,700 --> 00:24:04,090
past water assessment reports

661
00:24:04,530 --> 00:24:05,420
from the time

662
00:24:05,660 --> 00:24:07,570
the health products factory opened until now.

663
00:24:09,050 --> 00:24:09,900
These...

664
00:24:10,660 --> 00:24:11,260
These

665
00:24:11,260 --> 00:24:11,940
all passed.

666
00:24:13,290 --> 00:24:14,370
We thought about it.

667
00:24:14,370 --> 00:24:16,370
Maybe the people's

668
00:24:16,420 --> 00:24:17,570
burdens for medical bills

669
00:24:17,700 --> 00:24:18,740
are too heavy.

670
00:24:19,460 --> 00:24:19,980
Right?

671
00:24:20,660 --> 00:24:21,260
So,

672
00:24:21,530 --> 00:24:22,850
the Group gave it some thoughts.

673
00:24:23,460 --> 00:24:25,980
It said that although the villages
have not officially merged,

674
00:24:26,130 --> 00:24:26,770
right?

675
00:24:26,770 --> 00:24:28,530
In the humanitarian spirit,

676
00:24:28,980 --> 00:24:30,090
the Group decided

677
00:24:30,290 --> 00:24:32,770
to allocate part of its welfare fund

678
00:24:33,330 --> 00:24:35,420
especially for the medical expenses

679
00:24:35,460 --> 00:24:36,770
of Shuiwei villagers.

680
00:24:37,810 --> 00:24:40,500
Other than reimbursements from
the new rural cooperative medical insurance,

681
00:24:40,810 --> 00:24:42,130
the remaining sum

682
00:24:42,370 --> 00:24:43,570
will be borne by the Group.

683
00:24:44,740 --> 00:24:45,420
Also,

684
00:24:45,660 --> 00:24:46,530
these households

685
00:24:46,900 --> 00:24:49,220
would be given additional
nutrition allowances

686
00:24:49,530 --> 00:24:50,290
and subsidies.

687
00:24:50,290 --> 00:24:51,180
More money for them.

688
00:24:51,370 --> 00:24:52,220
What do you think?

689
00:24:53,570 --> 00:24:54,330
Agreed.

690
00:24:54,770 --> 00:24:55,420
Agreed?

691
00:24:56,370 --> 00:24:56,810
Chuanjia,

692
00:24:56,980 --> 00:24:57,460
well...

693
00:24:57,700 --> 00:24:58,130
I...

694
00:24:58,770 --> 00:25:00,940
On behalf of all the villagers
of Shuiwei Village,

695
00:25:01,050 --> 00:25:02,900
especially the sick villagers,

696
00:25:03,220 --> 00:25:04,050
I bow to you.

697
00:25:04,460 --> 00:25:06,020
Please don't, or I'll have to kneel.

698
00:25:07,290 --> 00:25:08,090
You

699
00:25:08,130 --> 00:25:09,500
have accumulated great virtues.

700
00:25:09,770 --> 00:25:12,370
Save one life
than building a seven-storied pagoda.

701
00:25:12,530 --> 00:25:13,500
Great virtues for you.

702
00:25:13,500 --> 00:25:14,740
This is what we should do.

703
00:25:15,260 --> 00:25:15,700
Mr. Li,

704
00:25:16,180 --> 00:25:17,850
if these people

705
00:25:17,980 --> 00:25:19,700
still want to sue us in the future...

706
00:25:19,770 --> 00:25:20,740
No way.

707
00:25:20,810 --> 00:25:21,260
Well,

708
00:25:21,700 --> 00:25:23,130
I'll talk to them when I get back.

709
00:25:23,220 --> 00:25:24,940
They will understand, right?

710
00:25:25,610 --> 00:25:26,090
This is a long-term project.

711
00:25:26,900 --> 00:25:28,420
I'm relieved now.

712
00:25:28,530 --> 00:25:29,610
Sit down and talk.

713
00:25:29,610 --> 00:25:30,330
Sit down.

714
00:25:30,500 --> 00:25:31,330
Tea.

715
00:25:31,770 --> 00:25:33,130
I have enough. No more.

716
00:25:33,130 --> 00:25:34,570
Don't.

717
00:25:34,570 --> 00:25:36,770
Hey, hurry up

718
00:25:37,770 --> 00:25:39,660
and get some desserts, tea, and cakes.

719
00:25:40,050 --> 00:25:40,660
Faster.

720
00:25:41,700 --> 00:25:43,810
I trust you absolutely.

721
00:25:44,290 --> 00:25:45,610
I'm counting on you, Mr. Li.

722
00:25:45,900 --> 00:25:46,980
It's settled.

723
00:25:49,020 --> 00:25:49,500
Okay.

724
00:25:49,500 --> 00:25:50,940
You don't have to see me out.

725
00:25:50,940 --> 00:25:51,370
Okay.

726
00:25:51,370 --> 00:25:52,220
Don't see me out.

727
00:25:52,610 --> 00:25:53,660
Okay, Mr. Mo.

728
00:25:53,770 --> 00:25:54,330
Okay.

729
00:25:54,330 --> 00:25:54,570
Goodbye.

730
00:25:54,570 --> 00:25:55,290
Mr. Li.

731
00:25:55,460 --> 00:25:55,740
Hey.

732
00:25:56,050 --> 00:25:57,770
Xingfu, you have things to do here?

733
00:25:57,770 --> 00:25:59,050
I am here to see Mr. Wan.

734
00:25:59,260 --> 00:25:59,810
Okay.

735
00:25:59,810 --> 00:26:01,020
Go ahead and talk to him.

736
00:26:01,330 --> 00:26:01,660
Okay.

737
00:26:01,770 --> 00:26:02,260
I'm leaving.

738
00:26:02,900 --> 00:26:03,980
-Bye.
-Take care.

739
00:26:03,980 --> 00:26:04,460
Okay.

740
00:26:04,460 --> 00:26:05,610
Yanping, drive slowly.

741
00:26:05,610 --> 00:26:06,370
Take care.

742
00:26:06,370 --> 00:26:06,940
Goodbye.

743
00:26:10,180 --> 00:26:11,660
What's up?

744
00:26:11,740 --> 00:26:12,420
Mr. Wan,

745
00:26:12,610 --> 00:26:14,180
here's the water assessment report.

746
00:26:17,530 --> 00:26:18,610
The Ministry of Ecology and Environment

747
00:26:19,050 --> 00:26:21,020
regularly assesses water quality.

748
00:26:21,090 --> 00:26:22,260
Do you have to assess it?

749
00:26:22,570 --> 00:26:23,460
Did you send this

750
00:26:23,610 --> 00:26:24,370
to get a reimbursement?

751
00:26:25,020 --> 00:26:26,130
What do you mean?

752
00:26:26,290 --> 00:26:27,290
What do you think?

753
00:26:28,460 --> 00:26:30,090
Why are you such a busybody?

754
00:26:30,660 --> 00:26:31,810
Without rhyme or reason,

755
00:26:32,180 --> 00:26:33,220
why did you introduce the teacher

756
00:26:33,220 --> 00:26:34,220
to the lawyers?

757
00:26:34,770 --> 00:26:36,700
You also took the lawyers to Shuiwei Village.

758
00:26:37,130 --> 00:26:37,460
What?

759
00:26:37,460 --> 00:26:39,260
To show that you know lawyers in the city

760
00:26:39,260 --> 00:26:40,090
and are capable?

761
00:26:40,740 --> 00:26:41,570
Do you know how much

762
00:26:41,570 --> 00:26:42,900
you have cost the village?

763
00:26:43,330 --> 00:26:44,850
A few millions. Do you know that?

764
00:26:46,050 --> 00:26:46,980
A few millions?

765
00:26:47,740 --> 00:26:48,290
Why?

766
00:26:50,020 --> 00:26:50,810
You won't understand.

767
00:26:50,980 --> 00:26:52,660
This report said that the water is fine.

768
00:26:52,660 --> 00:26:53,900
Why must you spend millions?

769
00:26:55,850 --> 00:26:56,900
Would you understand?

770
00:26:58,050 --> 00:26:59,900
Anyway, stop being a busybody.

771
00:27:00,770 --> 00:27:01,740
Are you here to deliver this?

772
00:27:03,180 --> 00:27:04,090
Okay, I got it.

773
00:27:16,530 --> 00:27:17,900
You've all got it.

774
00:27:18,570 --> 00:27:19,980
These are roughly

775
00:27:20,330 --> 00:27:21,180
the conditions

776
00:27:21,260 --> 00:27:22,290
set by Wan Village.

777
00:27:22,530 --> 00:27:25,460
Let's discuss them.

778
00:27:30,530 --> 00:27:31,180
By right,

779
00:27:31,740 --> 00:27:33,570
these conditions are very good,

780
00:27:34,220 --> 00:27:36,220
but what about the villagers who want a lawsuit?

781
00:27:36,740 --> 00:27:37,770
Talk to them.

782
00:27:39,330 --> 00:27:40,500
Settle with them first.

783
00:27:41,090 --> 00:27:42,370
We don't have solid evidence

784
00:27:42,370 --> 00:27:43,570
to guarantee that we can win.

785
00:27:44,900 --> 00:27:45,810
After all the trouble,

786
00:27:46,770 --> 00:27:47,290
I think

787
00:27:47,740 --> 00:27:49,530
even if the factory caused pollution before,

788
00:27:50,130 --> 00:27:51,290
it wouldn't do it again.

789
00:27:51,700 --> 00:27:53,220
The pollution problem is solved.

790
00:27:54,090 --> 00:27:55,740
It doesn't matter whether we sue them.

791
00:27:56,810 --> 00:27:57,700
A lawsuit

792
00:27:57,770 --> 00:27:58,810
takes time and money

793
00:27:59,020 --> 00:27:59,700
and disrupts harmony.

794
00:28:00,050 --> 00:28:02,260
It should be our last resort.

795
00:28:03,900 --> 00:28:06,260
They buckled when we talked about a lawsuit.

796
00:28:06,810 --> 00:28:08,330
That means something is fishy.

797
00:28:08,980 --> 00:28:09,660
Why don't we

798
00:28:09,700 --> 00:28:10,810
keep making a fuss?

799
00:28:11,610 --> 00:28:13,130
Maybe we can get

800
00:28:13,130 --> 00:28:14,260
better conditions?

801
00:28:14,420 --> 00:28:15,220
I doubt it.

802
00:28:16,220 --> 00:28:17,420
If they get annoyed,

803
00:28:18,050 --> 00:28:19,610
it'll be hard

804
00:28:20,020 --> 00:28:20,770
to get a good offer.

805
00:28:21,220 --> 00:28:21,980
We already know

806
00:28:21,980 --> 00:28:22,850
their weakness.

807
00:28:23,260 --> 00:28:23,980
What's there to fear?

808
00:28:24,130 --> 00:28:25,090
We can promise them first.

809
00:28:25,810 --> 00:28:26,420
Later,

810
00:28:27,050 --> 00:28:28,090
if they bully us again,

811
00:28:28,810 --> 00:28:29,500
we can still

812
00:28:30,370 --> 00:28:32,260
touch their sore point.

813
00:28:32,700 --> 00:28:33,610
Let's not rush it.

814
00:28:37,610 --> 00:28:38,810
I have no opinion.

815
00:28:39,530 --> 00:28:40,130
Neither do I.

816
00:28:41,050 --> 00:28:41,900
Okay.

817
00:28:42,130 --> 00:28:43,370
I'll say a few words.

818
00:28:44,130 --> 00:28:45,570
The higher-ups

819
00:28:45,770 --> 00:28:47,530
asked us to merge with Wan Village.

820
00:28:48,850 --> 00:28:50,530
Once we merge,

821
00:28:50,980 --> 00:28:52,130
we are a family.

822
00:28:52,260 --> 00:28:53,090
We eat from the same pot.

823
00:28:53,130 --> 00:28:56,570
If you shed all pretense of cordiality,

824
00:28:57,050 --> 00:28:58,090
in the future,

825
00:28:59,020 --> 00:28:59,700
things can get nasty.

826
00:28:59,900 --> 00:29:00,500
Am I right?

827
00:29:00,980 --> 00:29:02,460
How can we work together?

828
00:29:02,900 --> 00:29:04,500
Since they showed sincerity,

829
00:29:04,940 --> 00:29:05,850
we

830
00:29:06,020 --> 00:29:07,530
should quit while we are ahead.

831
00:29:09,460 --> 00:29:10,460
As for the villagers,

832
00:29:11,050 --> 00:29:12,020
we should go to them

833
00:29:12,180 --> 00:29:13,980
and do our best

834
00:29:14,530 --> 00:29:16,500
to talk to them.

835
00:29:16,980 --> 00:29:17,740
After all,

836
00:29:18,290 --> 00:29:19,660
we should treasure harmony.

837
00:29:20,330 --> 00:29:21,020
Yes.

838
00:29:21,020 --> 00:29:22,770
It makes sense.

839
00:29:23,610 --> 00:29:24,460
Is that Mr. Guan?

840
00:29:25,460 --> 00:29:27,570
I am Li Maoqin from Shuiwei Village.

841
00:29:28,180 --> 00:29:29,570
You must be the head of Shuiwei Village.

842
00:29:29,740 --> 00:29:30,850
Yes, that's me.

843
00:29:31,610 --> 00:29:32,330
It's like this.

844
00:29:32,900 --> 00:29:34,940
[Shuiwei Village Police Office]
I call you to say

845
00:29:35,420 --> 00:29:37,940
that we won't trouble you

846
00:29:39,500 --> 00:29:41,180
with the lawsuit against Wan Village.

847
00:29:42,260 --> 00:29:43,090
Do you mean

848
00:29:44,090 --> 00:29:45,050
you won't sue them?

849
00:29:46,330 --> 00:29:47,610
Yes, we won't.

850
00:29:48,740 --> 00:29:50,020
Look.

851
00:29:50,020 --> 00:29:51,900
Our two villages

852
00:29:51,940 --> 00:29:53,810
are talking about merging.

853
00:29:54,130 --> 00:29:54,940
After we merge,

854
00:29:54,940 --> 00:29:57,370
we are a family.

855
00:29:57,700 --> 00:29:59,090
Many people in our village

856
00:29:59,090 --> 00:30:01,460
want to work at the Wanjia Group.

857
00:30:02,370 --> 00:30:03,700
If we file a lawsuit,

858
00:30:03,700 --> 00:30:06,020
we'll have an acrimonious fall-out
and feel awkward meeting each other.

859
00:30:07,020 --> 00:30:08,610
Maybe we'll lose our jobs.

860
00:30:08,980 --> 00:30:10,850
Many people don't want to file the lawsuit.

861
00:30:10,980 --> 00:30:12,220
I understand.

862
00:30:12,660 --> 00:30:14,850
Good. You understand.

863
00:30:15,290 --> 00:30:16,330
Anyway,

864
00:30:16,770 --> 00:30:17,980
we are very grateful

865
00:30:18,370 --> 00:30:20,610
for the legal advice you gave us

866
00:30:21,180 --> 00:30:22,260
and your assistance.

867
00:30:23,130 --> 00:30:23,770
You're welcome.

868
00:30:24,900 --> 00:30:26,610
Mr. Guan, that's it for now.

869
00:30:26,700 --> 00:30:27,500
Thank you.

870
00:30:27,610 --> 00:30:28,420
Okay.

871
00:30:28,420 --> 00:30:29,980
If you need anything in the future,

872
00:30:29,980 --> 00:30:30,940
call me anytime.

873
00:30:31,260 --> 00:30:31,900
Okay. Bye.

874
00:30:34,740 --> 00:30:35,420
Shuiwei Village

875
00:30:35,420 --> 00:30:37,610
will merge with Wan Village soon.

876
00:30:38,130 --> 00:30:39,090
After the merger,

877
00:30:39,770 --> 00:30:41,020
they are a family.

878
00:30:41,740 --> 00:30:43,050
If they drop all pretensions now,

879
00:30:43,050 --> 00:30:43,660
the people

880
00:30:44,020 --> 00:30:45,700
of the villages will not get along well.

881
00:30:45,700 --> 00:30:46,530
Therefore,

882
00:30:46,530 --> 00:30:47,460
they decide

883
00:30:47,770 --> 00:30:49,460
not to sue the health products factory.

884
00:30:50,420 --> 00:30:51,660
Thank goodness.

885
00:30:52,020 --> 00:30:52,940
Save us the trouble.

886
00:30:53,810 --> 00:30:55,530
What do you mean?

887
00:30:55,980 --> 00:30:57,330
What do you mean by that?

888
00:30:57,940 --> 00:30:59,130
I seek truth from facts.

